graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        Frontend[Frontend<br/>React/PatternFly<br/>Port: 8080/TCP]
        Backend[Backend<br/>Node.js Fastify<br/>Port: 8080/TCP]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift OAuth<br/>Port: 8443/TCP]

        Frontend -->|serves| Backend
        OAuthProxy -->|authenticates| Backend
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources (CRDs)"
        DashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhApp[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhDoc[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        QuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
        AccelProfile[AcceleratorProfile<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        OSAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Components"
        Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>CRD: kubeflow.org]
        Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]
        MLMD[ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]
        TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS]
        KServe[KServe<br/>CRD: serving.kserve.io]
        Builds[OpenShift Builds<br/>API: build.openshift.io]
    end

    subgraph "Integration"
        ConsoleLink[OpenShift ConsoleLink]
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS 443| OAuthProxy
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OSAuth

    Backend -->|manages| DashboardConfig
    Backend -->|manages| OdhApp
    Backend -->|manages| OdhDoc
    Backend -->|manages| QuickStart
    Backend -->|manages| AccelProfile

    Backend -->|REST API| K8sAPI
    Backend -->|queries| Prometheus

    Backend -->|manages CRDs| Notebooks
    Backend -->|proxies to| Pipelines
    Backend -->|proxies to| ModelRegistry
    Backend -->|proxies to| MLMD
    Backend -->|proxies to| TrustyAI
    Backend -->|manages CRDs| KServe
    Backend -->|API calls| Builds

    ConsoleLink -->|links to| OAuthProxy

